name: Tiffany HardWear
description:
Tiffany HardWear is an expression of love’s transformative strength. Inspired by a quintessential bracelet from 1962 found in the House’s archives, HardWear embodies enduring resilience and uninhibited spirit. Handcrafted in Switzerland, each Tiffany HardWear watch features the iconic gauge links and brilliant diamonds. This 18k rose gold watch features pavé diamonds and a white mother-of-pearl dial. A hidden clasp creates a streamlined design, while a faceted sapphire-glass crystal evokes the unique shape of the legendary Tiffany Diamond. It makes a beautiful statement worn on its own or layered with Tiffany HardWear bracelets.

-18k rose gold with pavé diamonds
-Size medium

name: Tiffany Eternity
description:
Tiffany Eternity watches remind us to live in the now. Inspired by a series of vintage Tiffany & Co. advertisements from the 1960s and ’70s, the dial features a heart-shaped rubellite at 12:00 and different diamond cuts at every other hour marker: round brilliant, baguette, cushion, Tiffany True®, marquise, Asscher, pear, oval, emerald, triangle and princess. The watch’s crown is inspired by the Tiffany® Setting engagement ring and adopts its iconic six-prong setting—a beautiful complement to the halo of round brilliant diamonds that encircle the case. This white gold watch features a black brushed calf strap set with round brilliant diamonds on the buckle. This striking display of craftsmanship honors our heritage of offering the best diamonds in the world—then, now and always.

-18k white gold with a rubellite and diamonds
-32 mm round case with round brilliant diamonds on the bezel
-Crown set with a round brilliant diamond

A modern iteration of strong and elemental design, this 34 mm round watch is designed in stainless steel with a gray mother-of-pearl dial.

-Stainless steel with round brilliant diamonds
-Gray mother-of-pearl dial with diamond numerals
